less                                  macro                                 less

NAME
     less - file perusal program

SYNOPSIS

     lleessss  ffiillee__nnaammee [[ffiillee__nnaammee ......]]

DESCRIPTION

     The lleessss macro runs the handy file-perusal utility program of the same name
     in a sub-shell.

     The program lleessss is public domain software available through uusseenneett or by
     request from Certified Scientific Software.  Help for lleessss is available
     while it is running by typing hh, HH or zz, depending on the version.

DEFINITION

     ddeeff lleessss ''uunniixx((""lleessss $$**""))''

EXAMPLE

     lleessss ddaattaaffiillee

SEE ALSO

     _u _c_a_t _v_i _n_e_d

